{"tid":1353800,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[耐人尋味] 香港總商會尋日份聲明有啲大倒戈Feel","createTime":"2019-07-23T04:31:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T04:42:21.000Z","uid":265252,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9bb80a62b8930cf70237ca15fc27b6c9a6a53d9d","tid":1353800,"uid":265252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T04:31:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n總商會個個都舉足輕重，喺自己界別都有頭有面，主席係香港最有錢嘅印度裔夏利萊家族，理事會有<span style=\"font-size: large;\">李澤鉅</span>、會德豐吳光正個仔吳宗權，仲有中銀高迎欣、滙豐王冬勝、渣打洪丕正、港交所周松崗、國泰主席史樂山、港鐵金澤培、九龍倉吳天海、怡和彭耀佳、中電嗰阮蘇少湄，最過癮仲有行政會議林健鋒。<br />\n<br />\n今次竟然夠膽簽份嘢叫林奠撤回修例、成立獨立調查委員會仲要官員問責。政府最大嘅支持不嬲都係呢班重量級商界（當然唔係班鄉紳），今次林奠真係要驚驚&hellip;&hellip; <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1RjVYTq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1RjVYTq.png&h=2f0724c6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0238ada81911701ef7291eff360ca9782f553a10","tid":1353800,"uid":82853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T04:34:37.000Z","msg":"外資唔再信任一國兩制，影響到經濟同呢班人既利益<br />\n針唔拮到肉都唔出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9efe4bd4922b660de6c3c21abfbea6fe656d4c8c","tid":1353800,"uid":274771,"like":1,"di